text_raw:
1. These Regulations may be cited as the Sea-Fisheries (North Western 

Waters Landing Obligation) (Amendment) (No. 2) Regulations 2023.

title: purpose of giving further effect to Article 15 of Regulation (EU) No 1380/2013
heading: 2. The Sea-Fisheries (North Western Waters Landing Obligation)
text_raw:
2. The Sea-Fisheries (North Western Waters Landing Obligation) 
Regulations 2021 (S.I. No. 101 of 2021) are amended in Regulation 2(1) by the 
insertion after “19 August 2022” (as inserted by the Sea-Fisheries (North 
Western Waters Landing Obligation) (Amendment) Regulations 2023 (S.I. No. 
47 of 2023)) in the definition of “Commission Regulation” of the following: 

“and Commission Delegated Regulation (EU) 2023/828 of 2 February 2023”.

text_raw:
3. The Sea-Fisheries (North Western Waters Landing Obligation) 

(Amendment) Regulations 2023 (S.I. No. 47 of 2023) are revoked. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

20 June, 2023. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine.
